The company GeberitThe globally operating Geberit Group offers a unique range of products and solutions both in the sanitary technology sector and in the area of ceramic appliances. Products manufactured in Europe account for more than 90 per cent of sales.













Sanitary products from Geberit – form and function of the highest calibre



































