InnovationsGeberit AquaCleanGeberit MonolithInstallation SystemsSanitary ProductsSupply SystemsWaste and Drainage Systems






Innovative and reliable

Geberit products




With an in-depth range of products and systems, Geberit provides innovative solutions for most sanitary applications. Once installed, many Geberit products remain invisible to the end user. And they fulfil their function for many decades thanks to their high level of quality and reliability.
Increasingly, Geberit is also offering products that convince with convenience and design in front of the wall, such as the Geberit Monolith, the Geberit AquaClean shower WC, Geberit actuator plates or the Geberit element for showers.










